item.title: How do i remove ancients from the tab
item.dc:creator: @d4rk_n0v4 d4rk n0v4
item.description:
@d4rk_n0v4 wrote:

search for something that looks like this

setSidebarInterface(1, 3917); setSidebarInterface(2, 638); setSidebarInterface(3, 3213); setSidebarInterface(4, 1644); setSidebarInterface(5, 5608); if(ancients == 0) { setSidebarInterface(6, 1151); setSidebarInterface(7, 12855); } if(ancients == 1) { setSidebarInterface(6, 12855); setSidebarInterface(7, 1151); } setSidebarInterface(7, 12855); // what is this? setSidebarInterface(8, 5065); setSidebarInterface(9, 5715); setSidebarInterface(10, 2449); setSidebarInterface(11, 904); setSidebarInterface(12, 147); setSidebarInterface(13, 962); setSidebarInterface(0, 2423);
now change to this

setSidebarInterface(1, 3917); setSidebarInterface(2, 638); setSidebarInterface(3, 3213); setSidebarInterface(4, 1644); setSidebarInterface(5, 5608); if(ancients == 0) { setSidebarInterface(6, 1151); setSidebarInterface(7, 0); } if(ancients == 1) { setSidebarInterface(6, 12855); setSidebarInterface(7, 0); } setSidebarInterface(7, 0); // what is this? setSidebarInterface(8, 5065); setSidebarInterface(9, 5715); setSidebarInterface(10, 2449); setSidebarInterface(11, 904); setSidebarInterface(12, 147); setSidebarInterface(13, 962); setSidebarInterface(0, 2423);
